reviewText: Some of these are pretty tired.
Excellent buy and the most classic of love stories.  A must for your collection.

I only bought this set for Mr. & Mrs. Smith because I am a huge Carole Lombard Fan and I must say I don't regret it the movie was wonderful very witty. It had me laughing and that's hard to do. The other movies were good too.
Enjoyable day before yesterday love stories.

If you like old romantic movies and good prices, you will like this collection. I got this for my sister and she loved it. Due to it being old movies, don't expect it to be in great quality. Still worth it though!
